Goosebumps is a mobile gaming company that has developed an Android game available on 
the Play Store, where a curious goose embarks on a journey to uncover the truth. 
Interested players can get early access to the game by joining the waitlist, with a 
special introductory price of $2. For updates and behind-the-scenes insights, gamers 
can follow the company on Instagram at @goosebumps_.nw.